  lines:
  - Welcome back! After leaving the robot to do its thing, we have come to the conclusion
    that we need to learn more about machine learning.
  - We've come up with three common methods of machine learning that we will need
    to ensure the robot knows as well.
  - Fancy lending us a hand again?
